Processed datasets, dataset samples, manifests, derived tables, final run outputs, and checksums in this repository are provided for academic verification and school-submission reproduction of the associated paper artifacts.

The included processed datasets are derived research artifacts, not raw device logs. They may be used to inspect, verify, and reproduce the submitted artifact package with attribution to the project.

Raw experiment logs, private notes, local cache folders, failed experiment dumps, and machine-specific tracking-service paths are not distributed in this repository.
